activities:
Selfmark.com is a general interest site allowing users to express their unique identity through the design of a mark based on personality traits and other interests.  Selfmark uses information collected to (i) process user registrations, (ii) provide, enhance and personalize the selfmark.com website features and functionality, (iii) allow u
sers of the website to create a community around their individual Selfmarks, (iv) design and create user Selfmarks, (v) register user Selfmarks with selfmark.com, and (vi) to update users regarding the website.
